## Project Context

You are writing developer documentation for **Refold**, an enterprise integration platform with three core use cases:

| Use Case | Description | Target Customer |
|----------|-------------|-----------------|
| **Embedded Integration** | Build native integration experiences for SaaS products | Product companies |
| **Integration Projects** | AI-powered bespoke integrations (4-8 weeks → 30 minutes) | ISVs & Enterprises |
| **MCP (Model Context Protocol)** | AI agents interact with 200+ external systems | Enterprise AI teams |

**Workflows are the center of everything.** The core problem Refold solves is field mapping between enterprise systems and DAG (Directed Acyclic Graph) generation.

